column5: Happy birthday you ol' bugger! Just don't be peeing on anything that's still alive at the party tonight!  Be well and have many more!
Ah ... He's still just a kid.  He'll catch up to the rest of us someday.   Have a great time ... and remember nothing tomorrow morning.
Happy birthday Rick    Hope you had a great day
Happy birthday buddy I hope the plan of the day was to have some fun.   Art
